{
  "stem": "24470.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think I'll continue a little bit about that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So whatever I want to mention is just the beginning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh, with the chain that I sold for bread, I couldn't bring myself to sell the heart because it was the only thing from my parents.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, in the camp, after being shocked and after losing my m-- memory for the period of time that I lost and didn't recall anything from that, I don't recall thinking about my parents in the camp.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I also don't recall continuing that evening pros-- procedure with God, uh, in any way in the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Uh, I probably-- what I try to ex-- explain to myself now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was probably shocked and let the inner part of me to sort of go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everything that was happening, uh, with me then in camp was like out-- outer, flowing out on the outside of me and not so much inside.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Inside was sort of numb and put away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Uh, that's why I don't recall thinking about my parents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I recall working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We worked many, many hours during the day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was like a automaton, you know, doing what I have to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I remember singing to a child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We, uh, had a very strange and miraculous incident in my barrack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Uh, very early at our imprisonment, there was a child, a very young child thrown into our barrack.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Uh, and we hid him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe two and a half.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was hidden in a bundle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We heard him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wrote a story about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We heard cry of a baby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I thought that I'm going mad, because we knew that all babies were killed or destroyed or nonexistent.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But here it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
